:"2019-09-22T07:52:03.000Z","msg":"政制及內地事務局局長，你話呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:05:38.000Z","msg":"佢係可以啟動真普選嘅其中一位問責官員"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:08:35.000Z","msg":"【聶德權：若社會仍混亂 不宜成立調查委員會及推雙普選】<br />\n聶德權表示，如果社會仍然處於混亂情況，民間兩大訴求、即成立獨立調查委員會及落實雙普選都不適宜。<br />\n<br />\n另一局長聶德權，林鄭在前朝出任政務司司長時，聶在政務司司長辦公室任職半年，負責人口政策工作，盛傳與林鄭合作無間。聶德權以勤力和「熟書」見稱，加上與傳媒關係良好，故成為林鄭組班的不二之選。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權指出，和平表達意見是《基本法》所給的權利，「但是我們見到開始有暴力行為，與警方執法出現的問題，我們是很擔心」，形容為「極端暴力」，影響社會經濟、民生。"},{"pid":"dec1c87f8db484161da46a5e6ba44549df9e502f","tid":1586904,"uid":75823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:09:12.000Z","msg":"黑油好過爆玻璃"},{"pid":"cdcaaad8d9213c547c485ebab00d3b814290f532","tid":1586904,"uid":4736,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/khTAeL3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkhTAeL3.jpg&h=ee3ac5ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4db86e10f1a2695531ae10edab5b37fbf31765b1","tid":1586904,"uid":90601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:09:46.000Z","msg":"廢老唔打 撕紙狗唔打 <br />\n政府高官唔會係無辜啦掛<br />\n唔想俾人打就辭職"},{"pid":"a18b5ec5096286e0b1257939103c1d9f95007b1e","tid":1586904,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e16f395698d1a93676333835814cc4548c47ea0","tid":1586904,"uid":136226,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"e1d70da189ad3524bcba1cf600acc9435c32c7ac","tid":1586904,"uid":157653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FY8TLR6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFY8TLR6.jpg&h=23180f7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:10:18.000Z","msg":"仲可以安全行車<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":